result.notes: This survey was undertaken by Cefas as part of the CEFAS Historic surveys; ... Survey took place between 09/05/1979 and 29/05/1979 on Cirolana Equipment used during this survey : - Hand Held Gear Handlines Gurdies with feathers - Otter Trawl 78ft Granton Liner, Rubber bobbins, Polyvalent doors - Otter Trawl Engels 1600 Polyvalent doors, Liner - Otter Trawl Semi Pelagic GOV NOP rig, Cirolana Spec. Survey operations were undertaken on 61 stations 80 different species were caught on this survey
